[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說摩訶迦葉度貧母經",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "宋于闐國三藏求那跋陀羅譯",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聞如是：一時，佛在舍衛國度於君民，與除",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "饉眾、菩薩大士、天、龍、鬼神、世間人民無央數，眾會聽經。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時，摩訶迦葉獨行教化到王舍城，常行大哀福於眾生，捨諸豪富而從貧乞。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c09_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩訶迦葉時欲分衛：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c10_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若其未行，先三昧正受，何所貧人，吾當福之？",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c11_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」即入王舍大城之中。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c11_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "見一孤母最甚貧困，在於街巷大糞聚中，傍鑿糞聚以為巖窟，羸劣疾病常臥其中，孤單零丁無有衣食，便於巖窟施小籬以障五形。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c14_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉三昧知此人宿不植福，是以今貧，知母壽命終日在近：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c16_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若吾不度，永失福堂。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c16_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」母時飢困，長者青衣而棄米汁，臭惡難言，母從乞之，即以破瓦盛著左右。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c18_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩訶迦葉到其所，呪願言：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「且多少施我，可得大福。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c19_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，老母即說偈言：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「舉身得疾病，　　孤窮安可言？",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c21_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一國之最貧，　　衣食不蓋形。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世有不慈人，　　尚見矜愍憐，",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何名慈哀，　　而不知此厄？",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c24_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "普世之寒苦，　　無過我之身，",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願見哀矜恕，　　實不為仁惜。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c26_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」摩訶迦葉即答偈言：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c27_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「佛為三界尊，　　吾備在其中，",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c28_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "欲除汝飢貧，　　是故從貧乞。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0761c29_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若能減身口，　　分銖以為施，",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "長夜得解脫，　　後生得豪富。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a02_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，老母重說偈言：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a03_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「實如仁所言，　　生世無功德，",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今在糞窟中，　　不淨塗其身。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "飲食無分米，　　羸形而不覆，",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如今之極貧，　　施意與願違。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a07_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」摩訶迦葉重說偈言：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a08_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「母說處不悅，　　飢窮無以施，",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若其有施意，　　此則不為貧。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若復知慚羞，　　此則著法衣，",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如母此二事，　　衣食為備足。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a12_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世有顓愚人，　　俗衣寶穀多，",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無慚不念施，　　計後此大貧。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a14_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "惶荒設福德，　　可謂為希有，",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "信哉罪福眾，　　至誠不虛說。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，老母聞偈歡喜，心念前日有臭米汁，欲以施之則不可飲，遙啟迦葉：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a18_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「哀我，受不？",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a18_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」摩訶迦葉答言：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a19_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大善！",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a19_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」母即在窟匍匐取之，形體裸露不得持出，側身僂體，籬上授與。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉受之，尊口呪願：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a21_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「使蒙福安。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a21_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉心念：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a21_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若吾齎去著餘處飲之者，母則不信，謂吾棄之。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a22_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」即於母前飲訖，盪鉢，還著布囊中。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a23_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於是老母特復真信。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a24_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉自念：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a24_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「當現神足，令此母人必獲大安。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a25_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」即沒入地，更在虛空身出水火：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a25_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "半身以上現其水出，半身以下復現火出。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a26_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復變化改易，飛騰虛空，從其東出沒於西方，南北亦爾。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a28_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時，母人見此踊躍，一心長跪遙視迦葉。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉告曰：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762a29_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「母今意中所願何等，世間豪富、轉輪聖王及四天王、釋梵諸天？",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b01_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若復欲得須陀洹、斯陀含、阿那含、阿羅漢、辟支佛？",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若復欲得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提、阿惟三佛者？",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "悉可得果其願。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b04_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，母人厭於世苦，聞天堂上審為快樂，即啟迦葉：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b05_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「願以微福得生天上。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」於是，迦葉忽然不現。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b06_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "老母數日壽終，即生第二忉利天上，威德巍巍，震動天地，光明挺特，譬如七日一時俱出照曜天宮。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b08_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "釋提桓因即自驚悸：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b09_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「何所人者福德感動，將無此間有勝吾者？",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b10_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」即以天眼觀，此天女福德使然。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "釋提桓因即偈問言：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b11_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此女從何來？",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b12_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　　大光明照曜，譬如七大日，　　一時俱出現；",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b13_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "震動吾宮殿，　　威德難可當，",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "本修何福德，　　得來昇此天？",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b15_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時，天女答帝釋偈言：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b16_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「本在閻浮提，　　糞窟不淨中，",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "羸老兼疾病，　　衣食不充備。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三千大千土，　　釋迦文佛尊，",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b19_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "次有大弟子，　　名摩訶迦葉。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b20_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "哀矜從母乞，　　說法我心歡，",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "貢其臭米汁，　　施少獲願多。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一心供福地，　　願欲生天上，",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "棄身糞窟中，　　來生忉利天。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b24_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，天女即自念言：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b25_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此之福報緣其前世供養迦葉所致，假令當以天上珍寶種種百千施上迦葉，猶尚未報須臾之恩。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b27_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」即將侍女持天香華忽然來下，於虛空中散迦葉上，然後來下五體投地。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b29_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "禮畢却住，叉手歎曰：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762b29_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大千國土，　　佛為特尊，　　次有迦葉，",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "能閉罪門。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　　昔在閻浮　　糞窟之前，為其貧母，　　開說真言。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c03_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　　時母歡喜，貢上米𤄜，　　施如芥子，　　獲報如山。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c04_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自致天女，　　封受自然，　　是故來下，",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "歸命福田。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」天女說已，即與侍從俱還天上。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c07_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然後帝釋心念：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此女於閻浮提臭惡之中，以其米汁供養迦葉乃致此福，迦葉大哀，但福劣家不及大姓。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當作良策，於閻浮提詣迦葉所，興設福祐。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」釋提洹因即與天后，持百味食盛小瓶中，下詣王舍大城巷邊作小陋屋，變其形狀似于老人，身體痟瘦僂行而步，公妻二人而共織席，自現貧窮乞人之狀，不儲飲食、穀、帛之具。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩訶迦葉後行分衛，見此貧人而往乞食。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "公言：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c16_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「至貧無有，如何？",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c16_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉呪願，良久不去。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "公言：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c17_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我等夫妻甚老，織席不暇，向乞少飯，適欲食之。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c18_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聞仁慈德，但從貧乞欲以福之。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今雖窮困，意自割，捐以施賢者，審如所云令吾得福。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」天食之香非世所聞，若豫開瓶苾芬之香，迦葉覺之，全不肯取。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c21_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即言：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c21_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「道人！",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "弊食不多，鉢來取之。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c22_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉鉢取受呪願：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c22_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「施家其香普熏王舍大城及其國界。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c23_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉即嫌其香無量，即便三昧思惟其本，方坐三昧，公及母還復釋身，逕疾飛去，空中彈指歡喜無量。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉思惟即知帝釋化作老公，而為此變，欲增福祚。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「吾今已受，不宜復還。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c27_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」迦葉讚言，「善哉！",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c28_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "帝釋！",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "種福無厭，忍此醜類，來下殖福，必獲影報。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c29_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」帝釋及后倍復欣踊。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0762c29_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時，天上伎樂來迎，帝釋到宮倍益歡喜。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0763a01_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告阿難：",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0763a01_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此貧母人，一切世間無能及者，惠雖微少，福報甚多，以其苦厄興至心故，致無量福，福應之報。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0763a04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "釋提桓因天上自恣，而捨豪尊來下殖福，獲報難量，是以，如來說檀第一。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0763a05_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "閻浮提人愚癡可矜，其如此比有少少耳，汝當廣宣如來真言。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0763a07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛說是時，天、龍、鬼神、四輩弟子、比丘僧，興設大福而至達嚫，願及眾生，隨其志願皆得果報。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0763a09_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說經已，一切眾會莫不欣樂，稽首作禮。",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0763a10_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說摩訶迦葉度貧母經",
        "from": "T14n0497_001:0763a11_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]